N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1903.7 - Disclosure requirements of eligible applicants

State Regulations

The corporation shall require in its list of conditions
that the applicant submit the names, addresses and business backgrounds of the
principals involved and the nature of their fiduciary and financial
relationships to the project and each other, whether past, present or
future. Notes
